"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7680dd521ffa6620db5676da3a1c3b6ba2ae1755","tid":1472994,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6c057950ed65cc1fac07eb212cfe3471/tumblr_nfv4w34Uby1qcbtvqo5_250.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F6c057950ed65cc1fac07eb212cfe3471%2Ftumblr_nfv4w34Uby1qcbtvqo5_250.gif&h=74060c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a><br />\n<br />\n其實我地係唔需要洗佢地腦，甚至唔需要接觸任何人，要做既野只需要貼去多大陸人既地方都係廣獨／粵獨poster就得....<br />\n只要將廣獨思想文宣貼到通街都係，中共見到就自然對放自由行落黎有所顧慮，將廣獨思想輸出從而增加中共管治成本同時減少自由行黎香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cbc09p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Cbc09p.png&h=55d383ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴絲打可以用下面條link去印文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/u/3/folders/1x95q3KBq0_0HBlGnIRXLw8qzQEwxs-Rg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Fu%2F3%2Ffolders%2F1x95q3KBq0_0HBlGnIRXLw8qzQEwxs-Rg&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=b7c10d49\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/u/3/folders/1x95q3KBq0_0HBlGnIRXLw8qzQEwxs-Rg</a>"},{"pid":"f860c618ef33d5d143f4d7587044c9525772698d","tid":1472994,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"721811"},{"pid":"47f7f73e7f3adcbf8913d0317df1fe1b4ec93c5a","tid":1472994,"uid":46014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:12:34.000Z","msg":"816全民提款換美金大行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2349320942cb5d0e86997145c473e42a4d79eab","tid":1472994,"uid":46014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:57:38.000Z","msg":"816全民提款換美金大行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif